      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The Quartz Composer engine calls this method when it needs pixels. It gives you the base address, the number of row bytes, and the format. Then, you write pixels to the buffer."
